[11/10/2018 03:34:25] <font color="#ffffff">Richard.</font>
[11/10/2018 03:34:27] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Hola!</font>
[11/10/2018 03:34:27] <font color="#ffffff">-Zac.</font>
